# Simple pyramid

o Pyramid

v  0  1  0   # Top vertex
v -1  0 -1   # Base front-left
v  1  0 -1   # Base front-right
v  1  0  1   # Base back-right
v -1  0  1   # Base back-left

f 2 3 4      # Base triangle 1
f 2 4 5      # Base triangle 2
f 1 2 3      # Side front
f 1 3 4      # Side right
f 1 4 5      # Side back
f 1 5 2      # Side left
